title: Upkar
subTitle: Radha's elder son sacrifices his ambitions to ensure his brother Puran gets a good education. Despite this, Puran grows up to become a ruthless man.

title: Aakhri Daao
subTitle: Ravi, a burglar, leaves his life of crime behind and starts afresh winning the trust and respect of the local community. His life takes a turn when his former crime partner approaches him with a job.

title: Madhosh
subTitle: Young Raya and Soni fall deeply in love and secretly marry against their families' wishes. However, as time passes, Raya begins to struggle with the challenges of life and starts mistreating Soni.

title: Chehre Pe Chehra
subTitle: Dr Wilson, a scientist, develops a theory about humans having an angelic and a demonic side. He conducts an experiment on himself to prove it, but it goes terribly wrong, leading to dire consequences.

title: Parivar
subTitle: Gopal and Meena's happy family with their children falls apart when their daughter, Sapna, ends her life and Gopal gets arrested for the murder of Diwanchand, who is responsible for Sapna's distress.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Hamara Khandan
subTitle: Vishal, who hails from a wealthy Hindu family, falls in love with Ruby, a poor Catholic girl. While her father approves of the marriage, his father does his best to stop them from marrying.

title: Paappi Devataa
subTitle: Ram and Rahim become best friends after the latter offers shelter to Ram when he comes to Bombay. However, Ram is unaware that Rahim is involved in illegal activities.

title: Kudrat Ka Kanoon
subTitle: When the good doctor Vijay is falsely accused and imprisoned, his wife and daughter, desperately seeking justice, are terrorised and slandered by the harsh eyes of the society.

title: Muqabla
subTitle: Two dreaded gangsters call it a truce and become friends. The peace is broken when both fall in love with the same girl and neither is willing to sacrifice their love.

title: Muqabla
subTitle: Two dreaded gangsters call it a truce and become friends. The peace is broken when both fall in love with the same girl and neither is willing to sacrifice their love.

title: Ek Shriman Ek Shrimati
subTitle: Pritam, a young man, falls for Deepali, the wealthy daughter of a rich industrialist. However, she is in love with Ajit and plans to marry him but Pritam tries to woo her and win her over.

title: Dulhan Wahi Jo Piya Man Bhaaye
subTitle: Prem is in a fix when his grandfather demands to meet his lover, Rita. When Prem pays a street florist to masquerade as Rita, the old man quickly gets attached to the caring girl.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Pyar Mohabbat
subTitle: Prince Naresh Kumar Singh runs away from home and returns to his kingdom after 18 years with a new identity. However, he realises that his family is in shambles and a stranger is to be crowned king.

title: Jaag Utha Insan
subTitle: Mahant Chaturvedi did not approve of his daughter marrying outside of their caste to Gopi, and as such breaks off all relations with them. Years later, Gopi attempts to make amends by bringing his group.

title: Saathi
subTitle: Two boys are left to fend for themselves after their father falls victim to police brutality. They make a living through petty crimes, but things get out of hand when they cross paths with an underworld kingpin.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Ladaai
subTitle: A man is wrongly accused and jailed for 18 years. After completing his jail term, he confronts the judge who convicted him and asks her to find the real culprits.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Shehzada
subTitle: Bantu, a middle-class man, grows up being neglected by his cold-hearted father, Valmiki. However, his world is shaken when he learns that he was switched at birth.

title: Abhinetri
subTitle: Stage artist Anjana takes a break from her career after marrying the love of her life, Shekhar. As time passes, their individual expectations start to clash and put a strain on their relationship.

title: Love in Tokyo
subTitle: While in Japan to pick up his orphaned nephew, Ashok becomes locked in a romantic misadventure with Asha, a troubled woman who is a master of disguises.

title: Lav Kush
subTitle: After Ram returns to Ayodhya, Sita is forced to go into exile. She gives birth to twins Lav and Kush, who later go to Ayodhya to attain blessings of Ram and recite the Ramayan.

title: Andheri Raat Mein Diya Tere Haath Mein
subTitle: Two friends join the underworld to make money and to lead a comfortable life. Later, they realise the ill-effects of crime and want to lead a normal life.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Batwara
subTitle: Amidst the fall of princely states in post-independence India, the friendship between aristocrat Vikram and a peasant is tested. Vikram turns vengeful after his brother is killed in a peasant colony.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.
